The Lifespan Machine Source Code
Nicholas Stroustrup
Harvard Systems Biology

Important!  V2.0 of the lifespan machine software is in beta,
and is strongly recommended over v1 for all new installations.
For more information, please refer to git repository branch "flow"

V1.0 has now been released under GPLv3.  We are currently looking into V2.0 .

Major Revisions
10.17.2006: Dawn of history
2.24.2013: First commit to github
3.14.2013: Stability update, switch to mainline SANE drivers
8.1.2018: v2.0 branch is declared stable
7.25.2019 v1.0 branch is released under GPLv3.